.8, 1112.5, 726.4]}, {"text": "Stockholders’ equity", "bbox": [162.5, 730.6, 309.0, 747.3]}, {"text": "17,498", "bbox": [655.9, 730.6, 706.9, 747.3]}, {"text": "26,318", "bbox": [764.3, 730.6, 815.2, 747.3]}, {"text": "146,588", "bbox": [863.3, 730.6, 923.6, 747.3]}, {"text": "130,048", "bbox": [957.8, 730.6, 1018.0, 747.3]}, {"text": "374,790", "bbox": [1052.3, 730.6, 1112.5, 747.3]}, {"text": "The following items impact the comparability of our consolidated data from continuing operations:", "bbox": [162.5, 787.3, 946.8, 806.0]}, {"text": "• The results of META Group, Inc. (“META”) are included in our consolidated results beginning April 1, 2005, the date", "bbox": [162.5, 839.4, 1105.9, 858.1]}, {"text": "of acquisition.", "bbox": [181.2, 866.5, 292.7, 885.2]}, {"text": "• We repurchased 8.4 million, 14.9 million, 0.8 million, 26.6 million, and 5.0 million of our common shares in 2007,", "bbox": [162.5, 918.5, 1082.5, 937.3]}, {"text": "2006, 2005, 2004, and 2003, respectively.", "bbox": [181.2, 945.6, 525.0, 964.4]}, {"text": "• In 2003 certain long-term debt held by Silver Lake was converted into equity.", "bbox": [162.5, 997.7, 799.6, 1016.5]}, {"text": "• We had pre-tax stock compensation expense of $24.1 million and $16.7 million in 2007 and 2006, respectively,", "bbox": [162.5, 1049.8, 1077.6, 1068.5]}, {"text": "under Statement of Financial Accounting Standards 123(R), “Share-Based Payment.” We adopted this statement", "bbox": [181.2, 1076.9, 1089.7, 1095.6]}, {"text": "on January 1, 2006, under the modified prospective transition method.", "bbox": [181.2, 1104.0, 749.7, 1122.7]}, {"text": "• During 2006 and 2005 we recorded $1.5 million and $15.0 million, respectively, in pre-tax charges related to the", "bbox": [162.5, 1156.0, 1082.7, 1174.8]}, {"text": "integration of META.", "bbox": [181.2, 1183.1, 345.4, 1201.9]}, {"text": "• We recorded Other charges, which includes costs for severance, excess facilities, and other items, on a pre-tax", "bbox": [162.5, 1235.2, 1077.1, 1254.0]}, {"text": "basis, of $9.1 million in 2007, $0 in 2006, $29.2 million in 2005, $35.8 million in 2004, and $29.7 million in 2003.", "bbox": [181.2, 1262.3, 1083.3, 1281.0]}, {"text": "• We recorded pre-tax goodwill impairment charges of $2.7 million in 2004. In the same year, we had $3.1 million of", "bbox": [162.5, 1314.4, 1098.4, 1333.1]}, {"text": "pre-tax foreign currency charges related to the closing of certain operations in South America.", "bbox": [181.2, 1341.5, 935.4, 1360.2]}, {"text": "• We recorded pre-tax charges for the impairment of investments of $5.3 million in 2005, $3.0 million in 2004, and", "bbox": [162.5, 1393.5, 1084.2, 1412.3]}, {"text": "$0.9 million for 2003.", "bbox": [181.2, 1420.6, 351.4, 1439.4]}, {"text": "• We had pre-tax losses (gains) on investments or assets and associated insurance claims of $(0.5) million in 2005,", "bbox": [162.5, 1472.7, 1089.7, 1491.5]}, {"text": "$5.5 million in 2003, and $0.5 million in 2002.", "bbox": [181.2, 1499.8, 547.0, 1518.5]}, {"text": "12", "bbox": [162.5, 1560.2, 183.3, 1579.0]}]}